data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 6 bedroom 3 bath property with 2667 sq ft located on almost a quarter acre lot in the highly desirable Fountainwood tract! It's hard to find properties with this size lot, especially with such a great location within Simi Valley! As you enter this sought after floorplan, you will notice the beautiful travertine and wood-like flooring that flow smoothly with the neutral paint colors throughout the downstairs. There is also a downstairs bath with a shower and two downstairs bedrooms, including a custom bedroom conversion room with close to a 200 sq ft bonus area that could be used as a possible rental with its own private side access! Additional highlights include a separate dining area, an additional eating area off the kitchen, cozy fireplaces located in both the living room and the family room, indoor laundry, and a bar area off the family room perfect for entertaining family and friends. The home also has 4 additional bedrooms upstairs including a large primary bedroom with two separate closets and a dual vanity in the primary bath. Additional upgrades include a newer AC/heating/HVAC system with custom Nest thermostats plus dual zones for upstairs/downstairs, solar panels to save on energy, smooth ceilings, recessed lighting, and ceiling fans in all the bedrooms. The backyard is massive with almost endless possibilities! There is plenty of room for the family and kids to play, BBQ/entertaining guests, and of course plenty of room to add a custom pool oasis built to your liking. This home truly has so much to offer and is close to schools, parks, popular shopping areas, and much more! Come see today!
